Our Financing Solutions
Our team of professionals understands not only the finance industry but your industry as well - and what it takes for your company to succeed. Our experience in providing commercial finance solutions gives CIT the strength and experience to provide your business with appropriate financing services. 

CIT Commercial Finance provides lending, leasing, and other financial and treasury management services to small and middle market businesses.
CIT Commercial Services provides financial solutions to middle market consumer product companies. Our lending and receivable management services are designed to improve cash flow, reduce operating expenses and mitigate credit risks.  
CIT Consumer Banking offers a selection of products designed to help you reach your financial goals. 
CIT Equipment Finance works directly with small business, middle market companies, and government entities to deliver commercial finance solutions for the acquisition of equipment and value-added services.  
CIT Rail is an industry leader in offering customized leasing and financing solutions and a highly efficient, diversified fleet of railcar assets to freight shippers and carriers throughout North America and Europe. 
CIT Real Estate Finance originates and underwrites senior secured commercial real estate transactions.




















