      Notice: Because there is a risk that information transmitted via Internet email could fall into the wrong hands, CIT Bank suggests that confidential information, such as account numbers or social security numbers, not be transmitted via email. Instead, please contact CIT Bank directly at 855-462-2652. Thank you.
    

